Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,【OP】
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.86,0:00:16.87,CH_OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,0)}现在的你 全力支持着我
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.87,0:00:20.62,CH_OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而现在的我 也有了支持你的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.62,0:00:26.63,CH_OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使彷徨无助 我们也要结伴前行
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.79,0:00:28.75,CH_OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(000,400)}奔向未来
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.64,0:00:38.76,CH_OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然与朋友们嬉戏
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.76,0:00:40.52,CH_OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(000,250)}这样一路走来
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.85,0:00:44.52,CH_OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,却依然感到内心的空虚
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.69,0:00:46.69,CH_OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,受尽冷漠的眼神
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.69,0:00:51.86,CH_OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(000,400)}寄身于时代的狂风中
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.11,0:01:00.49,CH_OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(000,400)}勇气与不安 如影相随
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.54,0:01:08.38,CH_OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,400)}因此 现在就要用我的双手创造未来
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.84,0:01:14.55,CH_OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)}那些让我们受伤感到绝望的日子
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.80,0:01:18.89,CH_OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些令我们哭泣感到难过的日子
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.89,0:01:20.85,CH_OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,依然萦绕于心
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.85,0:01:24.85,CH_OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我们终将跨过重重障碍
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.85,0:01:29.11,CH_OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(000,600)}以超越所有人为目标
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.86,0:00:16.87,JP_OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,0)}君が今僕を支えて
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.87,0:00:20.62,JP_OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,僕が今君を支える
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.62,0:00:26.63,JP_OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,だから迷いながらも共に生きていこうよ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.79,0:00:28.75,JP_OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(000,400)}未来へと
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.64,0:00:38.76,JP_OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仲間と戯れ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.76,0:00:40.52,JP_OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(000,250)}それなりで居ても
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.85,0:00:44.52,JP_OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,もの足りなさを感じてしまう
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.69,0:00:46.69,JP_OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷めた目で見られて
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.69,0:00:51.86,JP_OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(000,400)}乾いた時代の風に吹かれている
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.11,0:01:00.49,JP_OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(000,400)}不安な心と勇気が背中合わせになっている
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.54,0:01:08.38,JP_OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,400)}だけど今なら夢をこの手で叶えてみせるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.84,0:01:14.55,JP_OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)}傷ついて壊れそうな日も
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.80,0:01:18.89,JP_OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,涙して困らせる日も
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.89,0:01:20.85,JP_OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,あるけれど
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.85,0:01:24.85,JP_OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,僕達はそれを越えていくんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.85,0:01:29.11,JP_OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(000,600)}誰より上を目指して
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,【ED】
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.18,0:20:49.06,CH_ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,曾经幻想 梦中的幸福{\fad(200,200)}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.06,0:20:56.02,CH_ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会有人亲手为我实现{\fad(200,200)}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.02,0:21:03.08,CH_ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在繁忙的都市中寻找藉口{\fad(200,200)}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.08,0:21:09.83,CH_ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人们都在编织着美丽的谎言{\fad(200,200)}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.83,0:21:17.39,CH_ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「你这样 真的满足了吗?」{\fad(200,200)}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.39,0:21:25.54,CH_ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在内心深处审视自己{\fad(200,200)}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.54,0:21:29.26,CH_ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果没能与你相遇{\fad(200,200)}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.26,0:21:32.63,CH_ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只会强颜欢笑{\fad(200,200)}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.63,0:21:39.70,CH_ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,带着虚伪的面具度过{\fad(200,200)}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.70,0:21:43.45,CH_ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为你眼中的坚定{\fad(200,200)}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.45,0:21:46.67,CH_ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我逐渐改变{\fad(200,200)}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.67,0:21:54.53,CH_ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了摆脱昨日飘浮不定的心绪…{\fad(200,700)}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.18,0:20:49.06,JP_ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夢に見ていたシアワセなら{\fad(200,200)}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.06,0:20:56.02,JP_ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰かが運んでくれると思ってた{\fad(200,200)}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.02,0:21:03.08,JP_ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,急ぎ足の街で言い訳ばかり{\fad(200,200)}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.08,0:21:09.83,JP_ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,みんなも同じとうそぶいてた{\fad(200,200)}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.83,0:21:17.39,JP_ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「本当にキミはいま　満足してるの？」{\fad(200,200)}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.39,0:21:25.54,JP_ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心の真ん中見抜かれたようで{\fad(200,200)}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.54,0:21:29.26,JP_ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,あなたと出会えなかったら{\fad(200,200)}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.26,0:21:32.63,JP_ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偽った笑顔のまま{\fad(200,200)}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.63,0:21:39.70,JP_ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,うわべの態度や言葉を繰り返したね{\fad(200,200)}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.70,0:21:43.45,JP_ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,あなたの瞳の力で{\fad(200,200)}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.45,0:21:46.67,JP_ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,私は変わってゆこう{\fad(200,200)}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.67,0:21:54.53,JP_ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨日の揺らいた気持ちを脱ぎ捨てるために…{\fad(200,700)}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,【注释】
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.98,0:02:58.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 NCC杯快棋赛就要开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.03,0:02:58.98,reference,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「NCC杯快棋赛」：原型为「NEC杯快棋赛」
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.01,0:16:31.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 国际业余围棋大赛我被选定为美国代表
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.00,0:16:31.83,reference,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「国际业余围棋大赛」：原型为「世界业余围棋锦标赛」
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.99,0:15:47.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,s—a—i
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.99,0:15:47.43,reference,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,sai是日文「佐为」的罗马音
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.61,0:11:55.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 我已经学会「征子」和「枷」的下法了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.67,0:11:55.87,reference,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「枷」：一种提子方法 不直接打吃而是从远处包围对方棋子
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,【对白】
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.13,0:00:03.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平安时代的棋师 藤原佐为
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.48,0:00:08.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穿越了遥远的时空 在进藤光的心中复活了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.34,0:00:11.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了领悟「神之一手」
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.04,0:01:44.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我输了…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.85,0:01:49.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前的你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.12,0:01:54.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甚至让我以为看到了「神之一手」…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.97,0:01:59.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs45\pos(362,384)}{\fnsimhei}{\bord2}{\i1}{\pos(362,375)}隐藏在网上的棋士
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.50,0:02:02.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我这样下怎么样?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.57,0:02:05.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是只把这边连起来比较好?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.58,0:02:07.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是如果他在这里叫吃的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.88,0:02:10.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说小亮老师要参加职业考试?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.78,0:02:12.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 没错啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.53,0:02:15.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是今天早上从室井先生那里听说的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.58,0:02:18.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是真的吗? 市河小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.94,0:02:19.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.82,0:02:21.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来是真的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.74,0:02:24.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那可是大新闻啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.76,0:02:27.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明年的围棋界可就热闹了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.07,0:02:31.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过这也太突然了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.39,0:02:35.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我本以为他今年肯定是不想参加了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.35,0:02:39.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小亮老师发生了什么事吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.73,0:02:44.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个嘛 我问他最近学校的围棋社怎么样了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.57,0:02:47.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是小亮什么也没说
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.55,0:02:52.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只说「那个已经不重要了 只是去玩玩而已」
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.71,0:02:54.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我也来杯茶
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.35,0:02:55.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 好的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.33,0:03:00.70,gogo2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\move(222,413,172,447)\bord0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\i1}{\fs19}第14届 NCC杯快棋赛 第5局
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.75,0:03:05.45,gogo2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\move(480,137,729,137)\bord0}{\c&HA9A27B&}{\fs20}第14届
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.75,0:03:05.45,gogo2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\move(480,199,729,199)\bord0}{\c&H685650&}{\fs20}NCC杯快棋赛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.75,0:03:05.45,gogo2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\move(480,241,729,241)\bord0}{\c&HA9A27B&}{\fs17}第1回合 第5局
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.04,0:03:10.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果您现在订阅一年我们的杂志
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.84,0:03:13.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们将会为您打折
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.68,0:03:17.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在也可以在网上下围棋了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.14,0:03:20.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来试试看怎么样?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.18,0:03:23.51,gogo2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(338,409)\bord0}{\c&H000000&}{\3c&HFFFFFF&}{\fr18}{\fs19}NCC杯快棋赛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.84,0:03:23.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯… 二十九 就是这里
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.34,0:03:33.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是离这么远看比赛有意思吗? 筒井学长
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.85,0:03:35.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,职业棋手会使用大型棋盘
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.96,0:03:38.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且会一步一步讲解给我们听的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.65,0:03:42.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是旁边的人这么吵
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.24,0:03:44.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下棋的人不会觉得很烦吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.17,0:03:48.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\move(368,22,65,22)\bord0}{\c&HA9A27B&}{\fr1}{\fs19}第14届NCC杯快棋赛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.33,0:03:47.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样才开心嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.24,0:03:50.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 好大的棋盘
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.39,0:03:54.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了 佐为好像也很开心
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.05,0:03:57.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马上就要开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.53,0:04:02.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现场的观众们 电视机前的观众们 大家好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.19,0:04:08.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第十四届NCC杯快棋赛第一回合第五局比赛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.71,0:04:12.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将在藤泽喜久夫九段和高田光一七段之间展开
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.96,0:04:17.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,村濑九段将为大家做讲解
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.85,0:04:19.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉永二段将为大家记录棋步
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.22,0:04:25.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么我们就马上进入比赛吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.89,0:04:29.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了 村濑九段
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.49,0:04:33.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你认为今天比赛的焦点将是什么呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.67,0:04:34.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs25}说起来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.41,0:04:40.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs25}藤泽九段在名人战循环赛以及本因坊战循环赛中的成绩…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.28,0:04:41.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是对不起佐为啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.04,0:04:44.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和塔矢的对局结果是我下了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.55,0:04:47.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{fad(0,200)}塔矢…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.51,0:04:50.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要试试
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.48,0:04:53.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己不亲自尝试是无法知道答案的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.79,0:04:54.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想知道
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.98,0:04:56.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己和这家伙之间的差距
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.71,0:05:02.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别胡闹了!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.75,0:05:06.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也对不起塔矢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.82,0:05:08.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他明明那么想和佐为对局
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.79,0:05:11.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.24,0:05:14.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我终于明白他的用意了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.48,0:05:18.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 接下来他会下到这里吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.83,0:05:24.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,二十五秒  六、七、八…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.75,0:05:25.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,4·十二
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.87,0:05:28.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 老师 您说对了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.98,0:05:33.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可不是站在这里瞎说 薪水可不是白拿的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.48,0:06:06.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过以后该怎么办呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.42,0:06:09.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然我也想让佐为偶尔下下棋
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.29,0:06:11.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可那家伙实在太厉害了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.95,0:06:14.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞不好我就成了靠运气获胜的棋王了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.18,0:06:20.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在的形势非常严峻啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.59,0:06:24.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs25}十秒  一、二、三、四…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.82,0:06:26.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,4·十三
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.86,0:06:28.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 下在这里啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.95,0:06:32.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕 完全没注意看
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.32,0:06:35.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个子被提掉了吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.07,0:06:40.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 不过他可能会从这里叫吃
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.63,0:06:42.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们来试着摆一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.67,0:06:45.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样下的话 这里 这里
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.10,0:06:48.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还要看下去吗? 筒井学长
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.00,0:06:51.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然要看下去 因为比赛还没结束…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.27,0:06:54.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去大厅里转转
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.71,0:06:56.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小光
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.65,0:06:59.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直一动不动地坐在那里看 我实在是受不了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.03,0:07:01.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.47,0:07:06.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可是一直盼着今天呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.74,0:07:09.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐为…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.29,0:07:14.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看 这里有卖围棋书的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.43,0:07:18.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那边好像也有人用电脑在下围棋
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.41,0:07:22.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 佐为 我们去看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.87,0:07:42.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是和你爸爸一起来的吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.96,0:07:44.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是 和朋友一起来的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.10,0:07:48.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是很少见啊 你家里有电脑吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.63,0:07:49.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.95,0:07:52.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你对网络方面感兴趣吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.98,0:07:54.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,网络?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.62,0:07:58.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 现在这个孩子就是在网上下围棋
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.68,0:08:00.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他执黑
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.81,0:08:03.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看 刚才他的对手下了一个白子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.29,0:08:06.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来又到这孩子的黑子下了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.68,0:08:08.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂 下那里的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.80,0:08:13.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.55,0:08:19.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在干什么啊? 这可不是电视游戏
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.97,0:08:21.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我得马上道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.60,0:08:27.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个… 不好意思 突然中断了比赛…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.43,0:08:29.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.17,0:08:30.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.34,0:08:34.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「你这家伙! 吃你几个子你就不玩了啊!」
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.68,0:08:35.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「白痴!!」
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.59,0:08:38.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先被他骂了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.26,0:08:40.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 真有趣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.17,0:08:43.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对方也应该是个小孩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.59,0:08:44.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小孩?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.04,0:08:46.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这家伙是小孩吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.00,0:08:49.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是他的说话方式和使用的用户名
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.74,0:08:51.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我觉得他很像个小孩
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.84,0:08:53.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用户名?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.92,0:08:55.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上网时用的假名
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.74,0:08:59.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,zelda啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.48,0:09:01.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来还有小孩啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.49,0:09:03.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在网上
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.62,0:09:06.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不会显示出你的相貌、年龄和真实姓名的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.38,0:09:07.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以也不能完全肯定
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.83,0:09:11.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不只是小孩 你看 还有外国人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.96,0:09:14.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,JPN代表日本
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.55,0:09:15.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,CHN代表中国
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.22,0:09:17.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,CAN代表加拿大
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.84,0:09:19.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有USA和GER
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.64,0:09:21.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那NLD呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.02,0:09:22.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是荷兰
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.87,0:09:27.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这个列表上的人可以邀请别人对局
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.32,0:09:28.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也可以被别人邀请对局
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.96,0:09:31.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,使用步骤和操作方法都很简单
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.63,0:09:35.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比如说 想找人一起对局的时候就点这里
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.51,0:09:38.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后再点这里
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.79,0:09:41.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想试试看吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.84,0:09:46.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是算了 还是先教我更详细的操作方法吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.75,0:09:49.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先要登录吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.60,0:09:52.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就从进入这个首页开始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.39,0:09:54.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.91,0:09:58.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先这样 进入世界围棋网 然后进行搜索…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.99,0:10:02.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs25}出现这个窗口后 然后再点这里…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.61,0:10:01.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不显示相貌、年龄和真实姓名
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.60,0:10:02.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是它了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.40,0:10:14.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 我下得不好还要让你陪我下
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.97,0:10:16.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.51,0:10:17.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果白子下这里的话
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.28,0:10:20.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该这样下吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.28,0:10:20.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.14,0:10:22.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.23,0:10:24.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.09,0:10:27.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下在这里可以吗? 或者下在这里?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.40,0:10:30.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种情况下哪里都行
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.91,0:10:32.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那这样行吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.89,0:10:34.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶? 就你们两个人?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.53,0:10:37.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,进藤呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.35,0:10:39.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他说去上网了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.22,0:10:41.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上网?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.43,0:10:42.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好快啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.49,0:10:43.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么好快啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.86,0:10:47.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天和进藤一起去看了一场职业围棋公开赛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.63,0:10:53.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可他说一直坐着很没意思 看到一半就出去了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.61,0:10:54.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.61,0:10:57.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那小光去干什么了?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.00,0:10:59.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是去上网了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.70,0:11:02.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不知道他怎么会对上网感兴趣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.30,0:11:05.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过有人在大厅里介绍网上围棋
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.73,0:11:07.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他就一直在听那个人讲解
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.44,0:11:12.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直到我看完职业比赛出来找他为止
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.74,0:11:24.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是他去哪里上网了?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.84,0:11:29.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是在三谷的姐姐打工的那家店里
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.96,0:11:31.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三谷的?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.04,0:11:34.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我姐姐在网吧打工
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.94,0:11:38.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我把地址告诉他之后 他就跑出去了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.69,0:11:43.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,筒井学长 你来下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.61,0:11:44.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 没关系的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.21,0:11:47.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.77,0:11:53.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藤崎你现在是不是懂点围棋了?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.83,0:12:01.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了 马上就要放暑假了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.41,0:12:02.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,围棋社怎么办?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.91,0:12:06.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要参加暑期辅导 有点忙
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.43,0:12:07.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.02,0:12:10.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,筒井学长已经是应试生了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.82,0:12:15.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小光从刚才的情形来看 可能会一直待在网吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.43,0:12:20.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还是想去那个围棋会场转转
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.07,0:12:26.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想去小光之前去过的那个围棋学校看看
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.61,0:12:29.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后下学期一开始
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.85,0:12:33.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要招收几个女社员 我也想参加大赛呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.08,0:12:36.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也可以去参加个人赛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.70,0:12:38.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 一定要团体赛才行!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.88,0:12:41.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上次看过你们比赛之后我就这么觉得了!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.41,0:12:44.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝对是团体赛更有意思!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.43,0:12:50.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说得对
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.81,0:12:54.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然我们输给了海王 但我还是很开心
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.64,0:12:59.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 团体赛的确很棒
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.13,0:13:07.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暑假的时候我们一星期见一次面吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.91,0:13:10.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样的话我也能来了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.72,0:13:11.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.31,0:13:17.31,gogo2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\3c&H000000&\move(227,361,227,215)}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\fs20}{\bord0}网\N络\N体\N验\N空\N间\N\N配\N备\N最\N新\N系\N统
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.88,0:13:24.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世界围棋网? 是想进入这个网站吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.41,0:13:25.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.42,0:13:29.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我虽然懂点电脑 对围棋可是一窍不通啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.35,0:13:34.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系的 我学过围棋的对局方法
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.87,0:13:42.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世界围棋网 搜索
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.47,0:13:43.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来看看
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.21,0:13:45.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 是这个吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.01,0:13:49.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,进入这里我就可以和全世界的人下围棋了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.19,0:13:53.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全世界? 你会英语吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.02,0:13:57.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会英语也没关系 只是下棋而已
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.07,0:14:03.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小光 你昨天就一直看着这样的盒子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.06,0:14:06.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然那个更扁些
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.26,0:14:08.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 里面的东西是一样的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.00,0:14:13.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是你到底要做什么呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.88,0:14:18.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想让你尽情地下你喜欢的围棋
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.99,0:14:21.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小光 刚才你说什么!?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.81,0:14:24.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别急 等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.80,0:14:30.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了 三谷是怎么学会下棋的?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.70,0:14:33.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爷爷还在世的时候教他的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.72,0:14:35.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他上小学的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.07,0:14:38.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有个会下棋的老师 他们经常一起下棋
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.88,0:14:41.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他毕业以后就去一些围棋会场转转
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.68,0:14:45.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佑辉很厉害吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.50,0:14:48.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很厉害啊 你不知道吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.75,0:14:51.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 这样啊 那你呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.29,0:14:56.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我? 我…普通水平啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.04,0:15:00.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,普通水平就想在网上和全世界的人下棋?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.39,0:15:03.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别这么说嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.02,0:15:06.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 和实力高低又没有关系
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.63,0:15:09.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那帮你进入到这里就可以了吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.88,0:15:10.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.87,0:15:13.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了 我真的可以免费吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.39,0:15:16.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系的 不过要保密哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.12,0:15:19.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且我不在的时候也不可以哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.67,0:15:21.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 知道了 谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.03,0:15:23.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回去的时候告诉我一声
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.12,0:15:24.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.77,0:15:25.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一会儿见
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.81,0:15:28.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后是 先起名字
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.85,0:15:34.81,gogo,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA00000&}{\fnsimhei}{\pos(151,265)}{\fs30\be1}姓 名
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.85,0:15:34.81,gogo,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\pos(500,140)}{\fnsimhei\be1}入会申请表
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.14,0:15:34.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂 可以尽情地下? 真的吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.74,0:15:41.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名字就叫…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.76,0:15:49.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,sai
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.64,0:15:56.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 开始喽
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.80,0:16:23.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈 我下个月要去日本待一个星期左右
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.43,0:16:39.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 大概有50个国家吧 一个国家派一个代表
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.06,0:16:43.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在国内的预赛中拿了第一
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.09,0:16:48.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然啦 还是亚洲最强啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.91,0:16:51.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日本 中国 还有韩国
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.35,0:16:54.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美国? 我们去年是第八名
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.34,0:16:57.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过多亏了网络
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.05,0:16:59.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世界围棋的整体水平正在不断提高
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.09,0:17:03.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,随时都可以找到很强的对手对局
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.02,0:17:08.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过听说日本现在的实力变弱了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.23,0:17:11.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 我会加油的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.99,0:17:17.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 说着说着就又来了一个挑战者
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.66,0:17:20.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那再见了 妈妈 注意身体
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.55,0:17:31.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,sai? 还是第一次看到这个名字啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.17,0:17:34.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就让我来看看你的实力吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.23,0:17:37.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了来了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.61,0:18:01.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师 和我下一局指导棋吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.97,0:18:03.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘘
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.26,0:18:08.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师正在为了下个月的国际业余围棋大赛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.30,0:18:10.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在网上进行特训呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.48,0:18:20.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不巧 那就没办法了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.30,0:18:22.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我来和你下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.10,0:18:25.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好 那我就不客气了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.61,0:18:50.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们这种水平是做不了老师的练习对手的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.73,0:18:59.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师可是连续两年代表荷兰参赛了 真了不起
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.63,0:19:03.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这哪算厉害啊 去年可是第六哦 第六名
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.18,0:19:07.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过今年可能会打破\N被亚洲选手独占鳌头的局面吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.66,0:19:10.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是老师的本职工作没问题吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.71,0:19:14.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他这么沉迷于围棋 还开办了围棋班
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.62,0:19:19.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 他可能会被开除 连教授的助手都做不成
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.02,0:19:25.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.68,0:19:36.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错 他是职业的 是职业棋手
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.77,0:19:40.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错没错
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.95,0:19:43.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在网上既不知道相貌也不知道名字
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.15,0:19:46.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说亚洲的职业棋手总是喜欢开玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.55,0:19:49.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会装成业余选手在网上下棋消磨时间
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.46,0:19:51.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.87,0:19:52.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.38,0:19:55.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.04,0:19:58.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,输了吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.98,0:20:05.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,惨败 对手好强 差点让我的心脏病发了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.42,0:20:10.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名字从列表上消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.58,0:20:13.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像是第一次看到这个名字呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.33,0:20:16.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,问了一下网友 谁也不知道他是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.34,0:20:19.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,sai  究竟是什么人?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.53,0:20:23.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好有意思啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.79,0:20:24.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.87,0:20:28.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那好 暑假我们就来网上下棋让你玩个够吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.55,0:20:32.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的? 我每天都可以来下棋吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.54,0:20:37.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 让你下到腻为止 做好心理准备吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.07,0:20:38.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,【GOGO】
